snippet.title: oddlly - Mobile Game Trailer 2019
snippet.description:
Dive into to the ODDLLY satisfying sci-fi world and Destroy your way to ODDLLY!

Our new game ODDLLY is on the Google Play. Try it out now!

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bullOX.oddlly
